<h1 id="about-secrets-of-christmas">About Secrets of Christmas</h1>
<p>Celebrate Christmas in this five reel, three row, and 25 bet line slot from NetEnt. Secrets of Christmas has three special features including a bonus game. The holiday spirit is everywhere in this slot. The mood is festive with falling snow, Christmas decorations, lit candles and Santas gift filled bag. Of course the music follows in the same steps.</p>
<p>If you like Christmas check this slot out and find out what Santa has left under the tree for you.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game features</h2>
<p>The three features in Secrets of Christmas are Wild Substitutes, Free Spins and last but not least the Free Spin Bonus Game. All of these features are triggered in the main game.</p>
<h3 id="wild-substitution">Wild Substitution</h3>
<p>Wilds function as any symbol except Scatter in this slot. The substitution always pays out the highest possible combination.</p>
<h3 id="free-spin-bonus-game">Free Spin Bonus Game</h3>
<p>The Free Spin Bonus Game activates whenever three or more Scatter symbols appears on the reels. During the bonus round the player selects gifts that activate different features during the Free Spin rounds that always follow the bonus round. The number of picks equal the number of Scatter symbols that activated the Free Spin Bonus Game. The features you can activate are:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Free Spins:</strong> Two, three four, five or ten extra Free Spins.</li>
<li><strong>Multipliers:</strong> An additional x1 or x2 multiplier is added to the starting x1 multiplier.</li>
<li><strong>Additional Wild symbols:</strong> The Candle and/or Bell  symbols are wild for the Free Spin rounds.</li>
<li><strong>Wild Reels:</strong> Reel two and/or four get covered in Wild symbols while there are any Free Spins left.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>After the Free Spin Bonus rounds we go straight into the Free Spin rounds. The default number of Free Spins are ten. The Free Spins plays with the same coin value and bet level as the spin that activated them. There is no way of winning additional Free Spins during these rounds. Once all Free Spins have been played through the game returns to the activating game round.</p>
<h2 id="game-details">Game details</h2>
<ul>
<li>Developer: <a href="http://www.netent.com">NetEnt</a></li>
<li>Reels &amp; lines: 5 reels, 3 rows, 25 bet lines</li>
<li>Bet levels: 1-10</li>
<li>Coin values (€): 0.01, 0.02, 0.05, 0.10, 0.20, 0.50</li>
<li>Minimum bet: €0.25</li>
<li>Maximum bet: €125</li>
<li>Maximum win: €50,000 / 100,000 coins on a single bet line</li>
<li>Hit frequency: 38.87%</li>
<li>Bonus game: Yes</li>
<li>Jackpot: No</li>
</ul>
